title: We're Not Done With James Charles - H3 Podcast # 242
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast Ethan and the boys get down with Dick Tips, discover a new sleep paralysis demon, react to Crazy Rudy freaking out about Lil Nas X's music video, and explore the LA Craigslist's "Missed Connections" page!
